{"tid":643220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺自己愈黎愈驚臭味同屎坑窿","createTime":"2018-04-26T10:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T15:48:36.000Z","uid":104086,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b607a69e022f9fc7bc3028fa1c4d3fdf57f2574c","tid":643220,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到乾淨強逼症Po 覺得自己都開始有一個病態<br />\n<br />\n事源上年開始成日胃唔舒服 <br />\n差唔多日日都嘔 每次一想嘔就衝去廁所嘔<br />\n咁一嘔一定係彎晒腰望住個屎坑窿黎嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果個時返工係商場廁所隔黎有少少臭就仲更加嘔到仆街<br />\n<br />\n慢慢開始好返少少 冇咁成日嘔<br />\n但開始覺得自己潛而物化左 屎坑窿=嘔 臭味=嘔到仆街<br />\n搞到而家一望到個屎坑窿就有想感覺 <br />\n係街到聞到少少臭都反胃 唔係大商場乾淨少少既廁所 係街係一定門口都未入就係咁反胃乾嘔 <br />\n<br />\n而家有一種愈黎愈嚴重既感覺<br />\n睇過醫生照過晒野都冇任何胃既問題 <br />\n身邊既人都會話 有冇咁臭咁誇張呀 但其實真係有<br />\n開始覺得係一個麻煩<br />\n同埋覺得係咪我心理有問題 身體本身係唔係咁嚴重<br />\n我係咪應該睇心理？<br />\n<br />\n示意圖 一望到個窿位就好辛苦 相都係 唔敢入去cap大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/185344_36a09c816ccf67b1d0e7502c5da6d7b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F185344_36a09c816ccf67b1d0e7502c5da6d7b6.png&h=bce8b824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f1987f27d6c836f6312fa65e46950a3d53d15b3","tid":643220,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"隨身帶支空氣清新劑 睇下改唔改善到？"},{"pid":"2f14de1747c67510afef81c9d0889ab5dcba5a2b","tid":643220,"uid":144858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"屌 點樣先可以將塊三文魚排跌落馬桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f21ec4d48e376ff7304320321e105422fa99be7","tid":643220,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1987f27d6c836f6312fa65e46950a3d53d15b3","tid":643220,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"隨身帶支空氣清新劑 睇下改唔改善到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"臭加假香味仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係街經過好難無啦啦自己係度噴"},{"pid":"ef1701fbec4c023440be34760995c2b1e8ec5f1d","tid":643220,"uid":12575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"絲？"},{"pid":"1cb8026636a7bf14be315de74761cf8603b726b0","tid":643220,"uid":173644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"閉氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由好耐以前 只要行近/入廁所 都一定閉氣"},{"pid":"579434610b3224622a1198e33418cdc63bca348e","tid":643220,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cb8026636a7bf14be315de74761cf8603b726b0","tid":643220,"uid":173644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"閉氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由好耐以前 只要行近/入廁所 都一定閉氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"而家係自動潛而物化埋啦 閉左都好易個感覺到要嘔"},{"pid":"50e84a91fc7b32d3e54508bf5676c1c97131f58b","tid":643220,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f14de1747c67510afef81c9d0889ab5dcba5a2b","tid":643220,"uid":144858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"屌 點樣先可以將塊三文魚排跌落馬桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81468502bcb53f7f5cf2be35e174722cb957bfb4","tid":643220,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1701fbec4c023440be34760995c2b1e8ec5f1d","tid":643220,"uid":12575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"絲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:42:09.000Z","msg":